{"tid":432211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！免入息審查《膳食津貼》指日可待","createTime":"2017-10-11T10:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T00:23:56.000Z","uid":111909,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3791953c0832cd4d900188dbe4dbb97541f768","tid":432211,"uid":111909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>衣食住行同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n有&quot;全民&quot;交通津貼 點解冇膳食津貼嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啊林鄭 你個交通津貼係&quot;全民&quot;同埋&quot;免入息審查&quot;嫁 我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n咩叫&quot;全民&quot;同埋&quot;免入息審查&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪就係赤裸裸嘅派錢囉  咪就係官［商］鄉黑都有份囉<br />\n<br />\n點有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有SMEs都會出翻張八達通比啲staff出外勤 物流公司都肥仔 又慳唔少錢 小巴公司暴利 買1萬張八達通翻黎瘋狂刷咭 水貨公司唔洗講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食飯唔重要咩 食飯都好貴 點解冇膳食津貼嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"12d0d6223b32c0d2cdd84205c948e41adf45b0e3","tid":432211,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef1b311131a1b02c63efe1bc3f7d723b9c986620","tid":432211,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"有得諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如：一個月食夠 400蚊麥樂雞，之後嘅麥樂雞錢就有津貼"},{"pid":"cdb8585316ae1488ac3fd4f03258954de9f8a730","tid":432211,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如：一個月食夠 400蚊麥樂雞，之後嘅麥樂雞錢就有津貼</blockquote><br />\n食夠400蚊麥樂雞，送番25%份量既麥樂雞津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2222c7b527487914898c6360f944a2faeab6bff8","tid":432211,"uid":26451,"like":0,"di